WEBVTT



00:00:12.240 --> 00:00:15.619
(Two weeks ago)
Tests confirmed terminal lung cancer.

00:00:26.839 --> 00:00:27.940
How long do I have?

00:00:27.940 --> 00:00:30.420
Three to four months, conservatively.

00:00:36.832 --> 00:00:39.980
(Huang Mantang)

00:01:24.260 --> 00:01:26.780
Huang Mantang, your life

00:01:28.560 --> 00:01:30.700
has been truly great.

00:01:32.680 --> 00:01:33.420
Mine isn't.

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:42.900
Look at me.

00:01:43.700 --> 00:01:46.920
Why has my life been so miserable?

00:01:53.680 --> 00:01:56.900
How come your life
has been so much better than mine?

00:01:58.500 --> 00:02:00.840
How come your life
has been so much better than mine?

00:02:01.420 --> 00:02:02.299
Huang Mantang!

00:03:18.080 --> 00:03:20.800
=The Silent Rift=

00:03:21.056 --> 00:03:23.784
=Episode 10=
(Turning Over)

00:03:23.840 --> 00:03:25.020
Now you

00:03:25.960 --> 00:03:28.020
are all big bosses

00:03:28.020 --> 00:03:29.960
and top dogs.

00:03:31.580 --> 00:03:33.340
But only I know

00:03:34.120 --> 00:03:37.840
the filth under your human skin.

00:03:39.620 --> 00:03:42.080
If you've got the guts, kill me.

00:03:43.340 --> 00:03:44.340
Do you dare?

00:03:56.960 --> 00:04:01.520
You're dangling me in limbo like this.

00:04:03.020 --> 00:04:04.620
Is it fun?

00:04:15.960 --> 00:04:16.579
Give it to me.

00:04:20.500 --> 00:04:23.519
Mr. Yonghui, Mr. Yonghui,
I'm Huang Daqing.

00:04:23.519 --> 00:04:24.019
No.

00:04:26.899 --> 00:04:28.600
I-I'm Chai Daqing.

00:04:29.180 --> 00:04:30.240
I'm your driver.

00:04:30.620 --> 00:04:32.607
I'm obedient. Woof!

00:04:33.439 --> 00:04:34.040
Mr. Yonghui.

00:04:38.592 --> 00:04:40.319
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:04:40.319 --> 00:04:43.620
Master, why are you suddenly asking
about Huang Mantang?

00:04:44.980 --> 00:04:47.560
Jiao Lijun confessed
there were four robbers.

00:04:48.980 --> 00:04:52.040
That means the witnesses
at the credit union

00:04:52.620 --> 00:04:54.360
could have had blind spots.

00:04:54.480 --> 00:04:55.680
Let's make an assumption.

00:04:56.920 --> 00:04:59.560
Meng Guangcai organized the robbery.

00:04:59.560 --> 00:05:01.620
Jiao Lijun and Wang Dazhu
both took part.

00:05:02.379 --> 00:05:04.740
Excluding Zuo Long
and Ma Zhongwu as decoys,

00:05:05.240 --> 00:05:07.180
could the fourth person

00:05:08.759 --> 00:05:10.439
also be someone close to Meng Guangcai?

00:05:11.680 --> 00:05:14.920
So you suspect Huang Mantang?

00:05:15.259 --> 00:05:18.000
Huang Mantang suddenly died
of illness in 2006.

00:05:18.759 --> 00:05:20.000
Let's make another assumption.

00:05:20.259 --> 00:05:23.360
That after the robbery,
there was internal conflict

00:05:23.819 --> 00:05:27.620
that directly caused
Huang Mantang's death.

00:05:27.620 --> 00:05:29.500
What else could it be?

00:05:31.500 --> 00:05:36.259
He was from our village
and got a terminal illness.

00:05:36.500 --> 00:05:39.180
Guangcai said we couldn't let him die
in the street.

00:05:39.420 --> 00:05:40.939
So we found a place to bury him.

00:05:41.259 --> 00:05:42.819
See, Master? A guy like that

00:05:43.259 --> 00:05:47.560
owns several businesses and manages
a labor agency with over 100 people.

00:05:48.560 --> 00:05:49.560
Who'd believe it?

00:05:54.360 --> 00:05:56.720
Forget him. Let's go to the mastermind.

00:05:59.712 --> 00:06:00.319
(6th Interrogation)

00:06:00.319 --> 00:06:01.620
Haven't seen you for days.

00:06:03.220 --> 00:06:04.800
Thought you got stuck again.

00:06:05.319 --> 00:06:06.759
You look quite comfortable.

00:06:08.180 --> 00:06:09.000
It's peaceful here.

00:06:10.759 --> 00:06:13.939
You don't know how many things
demand my attention outside every day.

00:06:15.620 --> 00:06:16.740
It's like a vacation to me.

00:06:18.920 --> 00:06:21.420
When you've investigated enough
and the term expires,

00:06:22.300 --> 00:06:25.160
finding such peace outside
won't be easy.

00:06:25.920 --> 00:06:27.259
Still thinking about getting out?

00:06:30.240 --> 00:06:33.680
Of course. I know your rules well.

00:06:34.759 --> 00:06:38.379
Look, you've had me 'visiting'
for quite a few days now.

00:06:38.560 --> 00:06:41.620
In a few more days,
even if you want to keep me,

00:06:43.560 --> 00:06:44.620
it won't be appropriate.

00:06:48.060 --> 00:06:49.740
Stop counting the days, Meng Guangcai.

00:06:50.759 --> 00:06:52.379
Today we're mainly talking about

00:06:53.500 --> 00:06:57.500
your old friend and fellow villager,
Huang Mantang.

00:07:01.240 --> 00:07:02.500
Huang Mantang?

00:07:03.220 --> 00:07:05.000
Between 1993 and 1994,

00:07:05.000 --> 00:07:07.379
Huang Mantang left Beiyan
and disappeared.

00:07:08.120 --> 00:07:09.759
He died of lung cancer in 2006.

00:07:10.500 --> 00:07:14.740
Caisheng Group's GM, Jiao Lijun,
handled his funeral, right?

00:07:16.439 --> 00:07:16.939
Yes.

00:07:23.120 --> 00:07:25.060
You're running out of ideas, aren't you?

00:07:25.060 --> 00:07:29.060
Anyone connected to me
becomes a suspect.

00:07:29.720 --> 00:07:32.560
Officer Zhu knows Huang Mantang.

00:07:34.160 --> 00:07:37.120
He was never liked since childhood.

00:07:39.800 --> 00:07:43.660
We handled his burial
while managing the company

00:07:44.360 --> 00:07:46.920
mainly out of respect
for Principal Chen.

00:07:47.620 --> 00:07:51.800
Meng Guangcai, quit circling.
Let's talk about Huang Mantang.

00:07:54.240 --> 00:07:55.500
Huang Mantang was simple.

00:07:56.439 --> 00:07:59.259
Officer Zhu knows most of his situation.

00:08:01.060 --> 00:08:03.680
In the same village as kids,
we saw him constantly.

00:08:03.800 --> 00:08:05.420
That year I came to Beiyan for work.

00:08:06.180 --> 00:08:09.939
Principal Chen thought he had no future
and sent him to follow me to the site.

00:08:10.379 --> 00:08:13.620
But he left soon,
complaining the work was too hard.

00:08:14.500 --> 00:08:15.420
When did he leave?

00:08:18.180 --> 00:08:19.379
I don't remember.

00:08:20.180 --> 00:08:21.000
I remember.

00:08:21.740 --> 00:08:25.240
During my site inspection in 1993,
you told me

00:08:26.000 --> 00:08:30.680
that he left the site in June
and went back to Shaguai Village.

00:08:31.560 --> 00:08:32.179
Right.

00:08:34.379 --> 00:08:36.500
But I didn't know where he went either.

00:08:36.500 --> 00:08:40.059
I thought he returned to Shaguai Village
to visit Principal Chen.

00:08:40.720 --> 00:08:43.840
He never came back to the site.

00:08:44.779 --> 00:08:45.720
He just vanished.

00:08:46.039 --> 00:08:50.159
He vanished right after the 6.10 case.
Isn't that suspicious?

00:08:51.460 --> 00:08:53.720
Officer Zhu, that doesn't make sense.

00:08:56.139 --> 00:08:59.279
Do you know how many construction sites
there were in Beiyan in 1993?

00:08:59.840 --> 00:09:01.340
And how many people came and went?

00:09:01.340 --> 00:09:03.639
In 1993,
Beiyan had seven construction sites.

00:09:03.639 --> 00:09:06.000
And 43 people vanished without a trace.

00:09:07.580 --> 00:09:08.580
So what?

00:09:08.580 --> 00:09:11.860
There were way too many

00:09:12.840 --> 00:09:14.259
coincidences, don't you think?

00:09:14.460 --> 00:09:17.740
After the 6.10 case,
you went to work in Guangnan.

00:09:18.240 --> 00:09:20.340
And you raised money
for Principal Chen's surgery.

00:09:20.740 --> 00:09:24.720
After the 6.10 case, Xue Qin's brother,
Xue Yonghui, got into a car accident.

00:09:24.879 --> 00:09:27.980
Also after the 6.10 case,
Huang Mantang vanished.

00:09:29.600 --> 00:09:30.779
Too many coincidences.

00:09:31.340 --> 00:09:33.159
So you've suspected me all these years

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:36.340
because of these?

00:09:41.779 --> 00:09:42.960
Officer Zhang, you heard him.

00:09:43.159 --> 00:09:46.860
Officer Zhu arrested me
based on these so-called coincidences.

00:09:46.860 --> 00:09:49.039
You know I'm not a smart man.

00:09:49.860 --> 00:09:51.519
I only use simple methods.

00:09:52.220 --> 00:09:55.279
All these years, I've traced
the movements of over 1,000 people.

00:09:55.279 --> 00:10:01.019
Only you, Meng Guangcai, have this many
coincidences surrounding you.

00:10:04.139 --> 00:10:05.620
Coincidences aren't illegal, right?

00:10:05.879 --> 00:10:07.039
Coincidences aren't illegal.

00:10:08.379 --> 00:10:11.000
But do you really think
coincidences can be perfectly flawless?

00:10:15.659 --> 00:10:17.500
Officer Zhu, you forget
what I do for a living.

00:10:19.600 --> 00:10:20.539
Twenty years ago,

00:10:21.620 --> 00:10:24.980
I came to the city to work and built
my business in building materials.

00:10:25.220 --> 00:10:26.360
Then I got into real estate.

00:10:26.519 --> 00:10:30.039
My whole life, I've been dealing
with bricks, cement,

00:10:30.340 --> 00:10:33.019
and other construction materials.

00:10:33.019 --> 00:10:34.379
Of course I know

00:10:36.139 --> 00:10:37.899
nothing is perfectly flawless.

00:10:41.980 --> 00:10:43.279
But think about it.

00:10:44.840 --> 00:10:46.779
It's these seemingly crude things

00:10:48.720 --> 00:10:49.779
that build houses.

00:10:51.279 --> 00:10:53.159
They make houses sturdy.

00:10:55.899 --> 00:10:57.220
If you put your heart into it,

00:10:58.360 --> 00:10:59.539
if you invest enough,

00:11:01.480 --> 00:11:04.899
you can make these seemingly crude,
imperfect things

00:11:06.360 --> 00:11:07.600
appear perfectly flawless.

00:11:08.899 --> 00:11:09.600
Isn't that right?

00:11:10.460 --> 00:11:11.340
Meng Guangcai,

00:11:11.720 --> 00:11:15.120
if you have committed crimes,
I can guarantee you

00:11:15.480 --> 00:11:17.279
we will find solid evidence.

00:11:21.480 --> 00:11:22.360
Officer Zhang,

00:11:23.220 --> 00:11:23.899
you still

00:11:25.279 --> 00:11:27.139
have a lot to learn from your master.

00:11:27.840 --> 00:11:29.000
Stay calm.

00:11:30.159 --> 00:11:31.720
You don't need to tell me this.

00:11:32.019 --> 00:11:33.100
You came to me

00:11:34.279 --> 00:11:37.019
because you lack solid evidence.

00:11:38.399 --> 00:11:40.096
Otherwise,
you wouldn't be asking so much.

00:11:41.500 --> 00:11:42.360
Right?

00:11:49.019 --> 00:11:49.860
Officer Zhang,

00:11:51.779 --> 00:11:52.740
I'll be waiting

00:11:54.360 --> 00:11:55.360
for you and Officer Zhu

00:11:56.480 --> 00:11:57.840
to escort me out someday.

00:11:59.808 --> 00:12:03.904
(Crack down on crime.
Protect the people.)

00:12:24.779 --> 00:12:28.860
- Master.
- Liu Hua's pushing you again, right?

00:12:33.539 --> 00:12:37.139
Master, Jiao Lijun's testimony
named four robbers.

00:12:37.500 --> 00:12:38.759
Why did it feel so natural?

00:12:39.399 --> 00:12:41.659
Something Meng Guangcai said today
reminded me.

00:12:42.700 --> 00:12:46.519
He said words don't matter,
and what matters is the action.

00:12:47.980 --> 00:12:50.980
I noticed Wang Dazhu
clearly got worked up

00:12:51.340 --> 00:12:52.980
when he heard 'four robbers.'

00:12:53.639 --> 00:12:54.480
Four?

00:12:56.019 --> 00:12:57.779
Four people?

00:12:57.779 --> 00:13:01.139
Then he immediately admitted Jiao Lijun
was also involved in the robbery.

00:13:01.700 --> 00:13:05.940
So Jiao Lijun's testimony
not only gained our trust

00:13:06.320 --> 00:13:09.200
but also signaled Wang Dazhu
to align their stories.

00:13:09.600 --> 00:13:11.240
If I'm not mistaken,

00:13:12.100 --> 00:13:16.360
their rehearsals were beyond
what ordinary criminals could manage.

00:13:16.860 --> 00:13:21.340
It wasn't just a script.
Every step was meticulously planned.

00:13:22.000 --> 00:13:25.480
So you suspect 'four robbers'
is a special code,

00:13:25.480 --> 00:13:26.360
and it's not true?

00:13:27.399 --> 00:13:29.379
Among the witnesses
to the robbery that year,

00:13:29.879 --> 00:13:31.759
besides the credit union staff,

00:13:32.639 --> 00:13:33.720
there was one more person.

00:13:34.740 --> 00:13:38.500
She remembered there might've been
four robbers. I have the record here.

00:13:40.860 --> 00:13:41.860
Who was this person?

00:13:42.519 --> 00:13:45.019
A little girl
who lived near the credit union.

00:13:47.899 --> 00:13:48.639
Here it is.

00:13:50.820 --> 00:13:55.980
She saw the robbers leave.
It was either three or four of them.

00:13:57.100 --> 00:14:00.019
The girl was probably terrified
and couldn't recall clearly.

00:14:00.620 --> 00:14:01.639
All these years,

00:14:02.500 --> 00:14:04.480
I've wanted to find that little girl.

00:14:04.860 --> 00:14:06.159
But without computers back then,

00:14:06.779 --> 00:14:08.500
we only got her name and address.

00:14:08.860 --> 00:14:11.600
When I went back later, she was gone.

00:14:11.720 --> 00:14:14.519
Alright, Master.
Give me all that information.

00:14:14.519 --> 00:14:16.000
I'll have the tech unit look into it.

00:14:16.740 --> 00:14:17.399
Okay.

00:14:28.159 --> 00:14:33.019
Master, it's been so many years
since the 6.10 case.

00:14:33.139 --> 00:14:37.340
I remember when I started with you,
you were already on this case.

00:14:37.340 --> 00:14:40.360
Now so much time has passed,
almost half a lifetime.

00:14:40.620 --> 00:14:42.899
You've put your heart into it.

00:14:44.928 --> 00:14:46.592
(People's police serve the people,
faithful duty ensures safety)

00:14:46.592 --> 00:14:48.576
(Beiyan Police Station, 2002)

00:14:53.259 --> 00:14:54.019
Go ahead.

00:14:57.139 --> 00:15:00.519
Dazhu, put your leg down.
This isn't your home.

00:15:04.360 --> 00:15:05.360
Officer,

00:15:06.100 --> 00:15:09.860
Guangcai really isn't here.
He's very busy.

00:15:10.740 --> 00:15:14.600
If you have anything to say, tell me.
I can represent him.

00:15:15.399 --> 00:15:16.019
Fine.

00:15:16.980 --> 00:15:19.940
Then let's talk about the situation
at your construction site.

00:15:20.240 --> 00:15:20.740
Okay.

00:15:20.740 --> 00:15:23.320
That construction site of yours
keeps having problems.

00:15:23.320 --> 00:15:26.100
Report says you beat people today.
What's with you?

00:15:26.100 --> 00:15:27.279
We didn't.

00:15:28.000 --> 00:15:31.340
It was those troublemakers.
They started it.

00:15:31.620 --> 00:15:33.700
We were trying to stop them.

00:15:34.379 --> 00:15:35.620
They just wanted to...

00:15:38.220 --> 00:15:40.159
Well...

00:15:41.279 --> 00:15:46.120
Zhu, look, you have such
a good relationship with Guangcai.

00:15:46.399 --> 00:15:48.139
It's just a small matter.

00:15:48.620 --> 00:15:51.220
Tell your people
to stop watching us so closely.

00:15:51.500 --> 00:15:52.519
You know how it is.

00:15:52.519 --> 00:15:58.440
Guangcai's company's biggest deal now
is renovating Baima Market.

00:15:58.639 --> 00:16:00.240
I don't care if it's a big deal for you.

00:16:00.860 --> 00:16:04.740
Dazhu, you arranged people to intimidate
those residents facing demolition.

00:16:04.960 --> 00:16:06.340
Don't think I don't know that.

00:16:06.340 --> 00:16:07.240
Listen to me.

00:16:07.240 --> 00:16:11.080
We're giving your company's person
in charge a warning and education. Okay?

00:16:13.120 --> 00:16:13.759
Hello?

00:16:14.120 --> 00:16:15.159
- Who do you need?
- Qin.

00:16:15.639 --> 00:16:16.360
Officer Zhu.

00:16:16.360 --> 00:16:16.899
Xue Qin.

00:16:19.820 --> 00:16:22.399
Tell Guangcai
that hiding from me is pointless.

00:16:24.159 --> 00:16:25.039
Zhu,

00:16:25.620 --> 00:16:27.000
Guangcai isn't hiding from you.

00:16:27.539 --> 00:16:29.159
He's just at his wit's end.

00:16:30.240 --> 00:16:32.460
You've seen him
build his business from scratch.

00:16:33.120 --> 00:16:35.940
To secure
this market renovation project,

00:16:36.500 --> 00:16:38.039
he's practically risking his life.

00:16:38.659 --> 00:16:42.860
We're short on funds now
and busy with the demolition.

00:16:43.539 --> 00:16:45.220
So some problems are unavoidable.

00:16:47.159 --> 00:16:52.100
We've known each other for years.
Why not come to me himself?

00:16:52.740 --> 00:16:53.379
Ma.

00:16:53.379 --> 00:16:54.019
Yes?

00:16:54.500 --> 00:16:56.460
Take them to get the paperwork done.

00:16:56.500 --> 00:16:57.100
Yes.

00:16:57.320 --> 00:16:58.120
Go with Ma.

00:16:58.440 --> 00:16:59.360
Thanks, Zhu.

00:17:00.159 --> 00:17:01.120
Thanks, Zhu.

00:17:03.580 --> 00:17:04.259
Let's go.

00:17:08.519 --> 00:17:11.579
I can't believe them.

00:17:12.980 --> 00:17:16.720
Weren't you focused
on the 6.10 case before?

00:17:16.720 --> 00:17:19.480
Why are you so concerned
about Caisheng now?

00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:21.940
Master, is there a connection?

00:17:27.079 --> 00:17:27.779
Gentlemen,

00:17:28.180 --> 00:17:31.000
(Report on New Baima Market Project)
about the new Baima Market construction,

00:17:31.579 --> 00:17:33.039
the district cares a lot about it.

00:17:33.980 --> 00:17:36.579
At this stage,
your most critical task is

00:17:37.299 --> 00:17:42.980
to complete the demolition compensation
for residents on the selected site

00:17:43.180 --> 00:17:45.279
quickly and stably
in the shortest possible time.

00:17:45.839 --> 00:17:49.519
Sir, this is our job.
You can rest assured.

00:17:49.839 --> 00:17:52.079
Not one will stay.
All will be demolished.

00:17:53.099 --> 00:17:54.200
Please be at ease, sir.

00:17:54.380 --> 00:17:58.000
During demolition, we'll stay
within bounds and keep it measured.

00:17:58.000 --> 00:18:01.079
We will make every effort
to satisfy the residents

00:18:01.079 --> 00:18:02.500
and reassure the government.

00:18:04.680 --> 00:18:09.759
I heard there's quite a bit of friction
over demolition compensation.

00:18:10.740 --> 00:18:12.500
To ensure better implementation,

00:18:12.500 --> 00:18:15.759
we've invited another company over
for consultations.

00:18:16.640 --> 00:18:19.519
You two complement and cooperate.

00:18:22.900 --> 00:18:23.880
Am I late?

00:18:25.240 --> 00:18:25.940
Rough trip, huh?

00:18:25.940 --> 00:18:26.500
Not at all.

00:18:26.500 --> 00:18:27.980
Come, let me introduce you.

00:18:27.980 --> 00:18:32.640
Mr. Nian, who flew in from Guangnan.
He's very powerful.

00:18:32.900 --> 00:18:36.240
This is Mr. Meng from a local company.
Get to know each other.

00:18:36.579 --> 00:18:37.920
Come, Guangcai. Come over here.

00:18:37.920 --> 00:18:39.880
Mr. Meng? I know him.

00:18:40.640 --> 00:18:41.660
Is that so? Come.

00:18:43.660 --> 00:18:44.539
Hello, Mr. Nian.

00:18:45.700 --> 00:18:47.339
Mr. Meng, long time no see.

00:18:57.079 --> 00:18:57.900
Come on.

00:18:58.279 --> 00:18:59.079
Come on.

00:18:59.720 --> 00:19:01.779
Mr. Zhang, come on. Mr. Li.

00:19:03.660 --> 00:19:04.500
Drink up!

00:19:09.700 --> 00:19:12.900
Drink up! Get the games going! Come on!

00:19:14.500 --> 00:19:16.980
Where are the dice? Bring the dice.

00:19:17.200 --> 00:19:19.700
Who's playing with me?
Entertain them well.

00:19:22.000 --> 00:19:22.799
Guangcai.

00:19:24.000 --> 00:19:24.740
How's it going?

00:19:25.740 --> 00:19:27.099
You're not drunk?

00:19:30.500 --> 00:19:31.740
These guys

00:19:32.799 --> 00:19:33.900
are all crafty.

00:19:34.339 --> 00:19:35.519
When drinking with them,

00:19:36.240 --> 00:19:38.400
I don't dare get drunk
no matter how much I drink.

00:19:40.740 --> 00:19:45.480
Is there any room left for maneuvering
on the Baima Market project?

00:19:48.680 --> 00:19:50.900
Dazhu, look,

00:19:52.099 --> 00:19:55.920
today, every faction
had at least one person show up.

00:19:57.500 --> 00:20:00.799
I'm counting
on keeping them well entertained,

00:20:01.339 --> 00:20:06.240
so they can put in a good word
for us on this project.

00:20:09.259 --> 00:20:12.980
We've bet all our money on that.

00:20:13.440 --> 00:20:14.900
We can't afford any mistakes.

00:20:19.519 --> 00:20:20.019
Mr. Li.

00:20:20.019 --> 00:20:21.740
Come on, Mr. Meng.

00:20:22.660 --> 00:20:23.339
Mr. Meng,

00:20:25.000 --> 00:20:27.700
everyone says you've got a sharp mind.

00:20:28.079 --> 00:20:30.299
You're truly something else.

00:20:30.880 --> 00:20:36.480
Who'd have thought of hosting
at a construction site? What a move!

00:20:37.440 --> 00:20:39.940
Today, we've really had our fill of fun.

00:20:40.299 --> 00:20:45.000
Mr. Li, just focus on drinking
and enjoying yourself.

00:20:45.240 --> 00:20:46.000
Here, to you.

00:20:46.000 --> 00:20:46.799
Let's drink up.

00:20:58.688 --> 00:20:59.864
(Caisheng Construction Company
Recruitment Resume)

00:21:02.180 --> 00:21:03.880
What's the need for an interview?

00:21:04.420 --> 00:21:09.160
Anyone recommended by you, Mr. Xie,
is exactly the talent Caisheng needs.

00:21:09.660 --> 00:21:10.299
Have some water.

00:21:10.440 --> 00:21:11.000
Thank you.

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:13.440
Tang, show Li around the company

00:21:13.440 --> 00:21:14.259
and fill her in.

00:21:14.259 --> 00:21:16.019
Sure, please come this way.

00:21:19.000 --> 00:21:19.759
- Okay.
- Here.

00:21:25.039 --> 00:21:27.240
My niece just graduated from college.

00:21:27.940 --> 00:21:30.480
She was little when her mom remarried
and took her away.

00:21:30.480 --> 00:21:34.420
Life's been pretty tough for her.
I hope you'll look out for her.

00:21:35.099 --> 00:21:36.900
Mr. Xie. Mr. Xie.

00:21:37.140 --> 00:21:40.000
She's one of our own.
I'll definitely look out for her.

00:21:40.579 --> 00:21:43.700
Don't worry.
She won't be mistreated here.

00:21:43.920 --> 00:21:46.039
Alright, I'm reassured. Definitely.

00:21:50.599 --> 00:21:51.339
Mr. Xie,

00:21:52.599 --> 00:21:56.180
about the bank loan,
you've got to help me find a way.

00:21:57.000 --> 00:21:59.660
I know you're tight on funds.
That's why I'm here.

00:22:01.299 --> 00:22:02.420
I remember

00:22:02.420 --> 00:22:04.700
all your kindness and help.

00:22:05.339 --> 00:22:08.500
But that loan amount
you mentioned last time

00:22:09.000 --> 00:22:10.920
is really a bit insufficient.

00:22:11.480 --> 00:22:16.240
Given our relationship, can you help me
get a bit more from your end?

00:22:17.299 --> 00:22:20.019
Based on your current collateral,
this is the maximum you can get.

00:22:20.180 --> 00:22:22.400
It should be enough
to ease your current urgent need.

00:22:22.759 --> 00:22:25.920
I heard you haven't even been able
to pay your workers recently.

00:22:36.940 --> 00:22:39.099
Xie Kaiyan abandoned us
after we helped him.

00:22:39.700 --> 00:22:41.680
We gave him so many benefits before.

00:22:42.240 --> 00:22:43.920
And he bails on us
at the critical moment.

00:22:44.019 --> 00:22:46.500
We helped him so much.
Why won't he help us?

00:22:46.680 --> 00:22:50.400
We have no choice.
He's got the bank's backing.

00:22:51.000 --> 00:22:52.740
We can't afford to fall out with him.

00:22:53.500 --> 00:22:56.660
This way, if anything goes wrong
with this project,

00:22:57.259 --> 00:22:59.000
we could be back
to square one overnight.

00:23:02.299 --> 00:23:04.500
We only had about
seven or eight families left.

00:23:04.500 --> 00:23:08.980
Now with this family causing trouble,
who knows how long it'll drag on again?

00:23:11.200 --> 00:23:13.299
Don't show me the contract.
I don't understand it.

00:23:13.400 --> 00:23:17.599
This house is for my retirement.
You can't tear it down. Leave.

00:23:18.000 --> 00:23:20.259
Sir, we've explained this to you
for over two months.

00:23:20.299 --> 00:23:22.299
We're strictly following
company procedure.

00:23:22.299 --> 00:23:25.599
I don't care.
No one could ever change my mind.

00:23:25.599 --> 00:23:26.900
Get out of here.

00:23:27.079 --> 00:23:30.819
Sir, please listen to me. Sir!

00:23:42.980 --> 00:23:45.779
Mr. Meng and Mr. Jiao,
this is the household.

00:23:46.079 --> 00:23:47.420
Can't negotiate. How are we...

00:23:47.420 --> 00:23:50.599
You can't? You can't?
If you can't, find a way.

00:23:50.599 --> 00:23:52.099
Can't find a way? Kneel at his door!

00:23:52.099 --> 00:23:53.180
- Guangcai!
- Get it done.

00:23:53.180 --> 00:23:53.759
Guangcai!

00:23:53.940 --> 00:23:54.440
You hear me?

00:23:54.440 --> 00:23:54.980
Guangcai!

00:23:55.160 --> 00:23:56.400
Get lost.

00:24:02.660 --> 00:24:03.779
Alright, calm down.

00:24:06.500 --> 00:24:11.279
Guangcai, give me three days.
I'll get him to sign.

00:24:12.240 --> 00:24:13.420
What three days?

00:24:14.480 --> 00:24:17.200
Zhu Helai is already onto me
because of what you pulled before.

00:24:17.880 --> 00:24:20.039
We can't let him catch us
on anything else now.

00:24:22.279 --> 00:24:24.339
Can't be soft. Not allowed to be hard.

00:24:24.339 --> 00:24:25.700
Then I'm really out of ideas.

00:24:31.180 --> 00:24:31.980
- Please eat.
- Okay.

00:24:37.980 --> 00:24:40.000
Everyone, I'd like to propose a toast.

00:24:40.420 --> 00:24:42.400
On behalf of Caisheng Group,
thank you all.

00:24:42.740 --> 00:24:46.240
We owe our achievements
to your attention and support.

00:24:46.980 --> 00:24:49.740
I hope you all have a great night.
Eat well, drink well.

00:24:49.799 --> 00:24:50.660
I'll drink first.

00:24:51.079 --> 00:24:52.539
- Good!
- Cheers!

00:24:55.759 --> 00:24:58.079
Everyone, my apologies.

00:24:58.079 --> 00:25:00.759
I'm truly sorry for being late.
Something came up.

00:25:01.140 --> 00:25:02.839
Mr. Meng,
I have to call you out on this.

00:25:02.980 --> 00:25:05.279
You invite everyone to dinner,
yet you show up late.

00:25:05.279 --> 00:25:06.779
That's no way to treat your guests.

00:25:07.039 --> 00:25:09.480
I also invited a few friends,
all people you know.

00:25:10.200 --> 00:25:11.039
Please sit.

00:25:11.640 --> 00:25:12.140
Sit.

00:25:13.019 --> 00:25:14.019
Go on, please.

00:25:15.579 --> 00:25:19.259
Alright, now that the host is here,
let me propose a toast.

00:25:20.259 --> 00:25:23.440
It's been years since I left Beiyan.
I've missed you all dearly.

00:25:23.660 --> 00:25:26.440
Coming back today,
I see Beiyan has changed a lot.

00:25:26.539 --> 00:25:28.420
And all you guys
are doing very well too.

00:25:28.420 --> 00:25:30.140
This makes me especially happy.

00:25:30.200 --> 00:25:32.779
So, let's all drink together. Cheers!

00:25:32.779 --> 00:25:34.259
Cheers!

00:25:34.259 --> 00:25:35.519
- Cheers!
- Cheers!

00:25:35.519 --> 00:25:36.019
Cheers!

00:25:39.420 --> 00:25:39.920
There.

00:25:42.259 --> 00:25:43.940
I'd like to propose this second toast

00:25:44.339 --> 00:25:48.700
to congratulate Mr. Meng
for securing Beiyan's key project.

00:25:48.900 --> 00:25:51.400
This is a truly celebratory event.
Here's to it.

00:25:51.400 --> 00:25:53.440
- Come on.
- Congratulations, Mr. Meng.

00:25:53.940 --> 00:25:54.920
Come on.

00:25:55.539 --> 00:25:56.660
- Congratulations.
- Congratulations.

00:25:56.660 --> 00:25:57.200
Congrats.

00:25:57.200 --> 00:25:57.700
Cheers.

00:26:01.740 --> 00:26:06.339
But Mr. Meng, I heard your demolition
is running behind schedule, right?

00:26:06.640 --> 00:26:08.259
And you can't pay the workers' wages?

00:26:08.740 --> 00:26:09.400
Don't worry.

00:26:09.400 --> 00:26:12.279
If you're in trouble,
you can just tell me.

00:26:12.660 --> 00:26:13.579
Don't be a stranger.

00:26:14.880 --> 00:26:15.900
Nothing like that.

00:26:17.839 --> 00:26:19.180
I'm just puzzled.

00:26:19.900 --> 00:26:23.160
It's just a small renovation project
on a market.

00:26:23.160 --> 00:26:25.079
Why are you so concerned, Mr. Nian?

00:26:25.579 --> 00:26:27.720
Like I said, don't be a stranger.

00:26:27.720 --> 00:26:29.400
Your business is my business.

00:26:29.519 --> 00:26:31.400
After all, you worked for me
back in the day.

00:26:33.180 --> 00:26:35.420
Back when I was building
the Eagle Building,

00:26:35.779 --> 00:26:39.400
Mr. Meng and his two brothers
work on my construction site.

00:26:39.700 --> 00:26:40.500
Right, Mr. Meng?

00:26:41.480 --> 00:26:44.880
But I think you look bad in a suit.

00:26:45.160 --> 00:26:49.000
I still prefer how you looked
setting off firecrackers.

00:26:50.240 --> 00:26:52.420
Come on, let's drink.

00:26:52.420 --> 00:26:53.640
A toast to Mr. Meng. Come on.

00:26:53.640 --> 00:26:54.140
Okay.

00:26:54.140 --> 00:26:54.900
Come on.

00:26:54.900 --> 00:26:56.079
- Mr. Meng.
- Mr. Meng.

00:26:57.559 --> 00:26:58.059
Come on.

00:26:58.279 --> 00:26:59.000
Come on.

00:27:00.039 --> 00:27:00.539
Come on.

00:27:00.539 --> 00:27:01.259
Come on, Mr. Meng.

00:27:03.839 --> 00:27:04.579
Come on, have one.

00:27:27.700 --> 00:27:28.400
Mr. Nian.

00:27:29.880 --> 00:27:31.380
You sure you want to cut in?

00:27:32.000 --> 00:27:33.600
Don't bite off more than you can chew.

00:27:37.140 --> 00:27:39.140
If I dare to bite, I can stomach it.

00:27:39.900 --> 00:27:43.500
Don't be stingy.
Just bring on whatever you have.

00:27:54.759 --> 00:27:56.640
I said, leave me alone for a while.

00:28:06.079 --> 00:28:07.099
Why are you here?

00:28:08.660 --> 00:28:10.656
You haven't been home for two days.
I was worried.

00:28:12.839 --> 00:28:13.660
Where's Xiaoliang?

00:28:14.000 --> 00:28:15.140
Sent to Mr. Chen's.

00:28:16.259 --> 00:28:18.660
You're off these days.
Don't let him see you like this.

00:28:25.079 --> 00:28:26.299
Lijun told me everything.

00:28:28.160 --> 00:28:29.920
I put the place up as collateral.

00:28:31.579 --> 00:28:34.579
The money's in there.
It should last for a while.

00:28:45.980 --> 00:28:46.839
Qin,

00:28:49.660 --> 00:28:51.400
do you think I'm too reckless?

00:28:54.519 --> 00:28:56.440
All the money I've earned
over the years,

00:28:57.380 --> 00:29:00.900
plus the money borrowed
from the bank, is tied up in this.

00:29:02.900 --> 00:29:04.099
This time, it's either succeed

00:29:06.640 --> 00:29:07.680
or die.

00:29:12.200 --> 00:29:15.200
If we just solve
the demolition issue quickly,

00:29:16.420 --> 00:29:17.680
we'll be okay, right?

00:29:21.500 --> 00:29:23.259
Moving faster reduces the risk.

00:29:25.440 --> 00:29:26.920
If others catch up,

00:29:29.339 --> 00:29:30.640
we're out.

00:29:40.640 --> 00:29:42.440
I'll handle the demolition.

00:29:46.000 --> 00:29:49.240
Without the compensation money,
no one could help you.

00:29:49.259 --> 00:29:52.099
Get out of here. Just go.

00:29:57.000 --> 00:29:58.799
Qin, what did I tell you?

00:29:59.299 --> 00:30:00.700
Being soft with them doesn't work.

00:30:00.700 --> 00:30:03.660
They're demanding more and more.
We've been too kind to them.

00:30:06.519 --> 00:30:08.160
Qin, no more talking?

00:30:27.839 --> 00:30:30.000
Huifen, get ready for dinner.

00:30:31.500 --> 00:30:32.259
Still writing?

00:30:38.395 --> 00:30:40.361
(Caisheng Construction Company
Job Application Form)

00:30:40.759 --> 00:30:42.519
You applied to this company?

00:30:44.019 --> 00:30:46.980
It's newly established.
The salary and benefits are good.

00:30:46.980 --> 00:30:47.660
Plus many jobs.

00:30:47.660 --> 00:30:48.940
It's Meng Guangcai's company.

00:30:51.160 --> 00:30:53.900
Guangcai? I wondered why he
hasn't come lately. He's a big boss now?

00:30:53.900 --> 00:30:55.980
You can go to any company
except this one.

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:58.500
I'm not asking for any favors.

00:30:58.500 --> 00:30:59.440
Why can't I?

00:30:59.440 --> 00:31:03.000
Any other place is fine.
Meng Guangcai's company? Absolutely not.

00:31:05.759 --> 00:31:07.480
Why are you getting so worked up?

00:31:08.980 --> 00:31:11.240
I told you before, you don't need
to work or earn money.

00:31:11.240 --> 00:31:12.339
My job's enough.

00:31:12.599 --> 00:31:13.759
Your job is enough?

00:31:13.900 --> 00:31:16.200
Relying on your meager salary
to support this family?

00:31:16.680 --> 00:31:18.200
Then wouldn't this family be ruined?

00:31:18.420 --> 00:31:19.940
I don't want to be useless.

00:31:19.940 --> 00:31:21.500
You can apply to any company you want.

00:31:21.700 --> 00:31:23.400
But not Meng Guangcai's company.

00:31:23.660 --> 00:31:25.299
What if I want to have a child later?

00:31:26.339 --> 00:31:27.759
What if I want to have a child?

00:31:30.039 --> 00:31:32.779
Before, you said Qianqian was young
and we'd wait until she grew up.

00:31:32.779 --> 00:31:34.799
Now Qianqian's grown up.
Can't I have one?

00:31:35.920 --> 00:31:37.240
Didn't we agree to drop it?

00:31:37.240 --> 00:31:38.400
Why should I drop it?

00:31:38.680 --> 00:31:40.279
What's wrong with wanting my own child?

00:31:40.279 --> 00:31:41.660
I just want to save some money.

00:31:41.660 --> 00:31:44.380
We can have a kid once we save enough.
What's wrong with that?

00:32:16.519 --> 00:32:18.279
You know why my brother Lin Shan,

00:32:20.480 --> 00:32:22.539
Qianqian's father, fell?

00:32:23.279 --> 00:32:24.160
I know.

00:32:26.279 --> 00:32:28.160
It's due to the 6.10 case
you're working on.

00:32:28.519 --> 00:32:29.240
Right.

00:32:32.160 --> 00:32:33.519
Do you know who was responsible?

00:32:35.599 --> 00:32:37.400
I've been working
on the 6.10 case for years.

00:32:37.900 --> 00:32:39.920
I have a clear suspect in mind.

00:32:42.660 --> 00:32:44.160
Do you know Meng Guangcai...

00:32:48.660 --> 00:32:51.160
The case is connected to Meng Guangcai?

00:32:53.980 --> 00:32:54.599
Yes.

00:32:58.779 --> 00:33:00.000
He's a robber?

00:33:07.480 --> 00:33:09.700
That's why I forbid you
from going to his company.

00:33:10.940 --> 00:33:12.160
You can work for anyone else.

00:33:12.160 --> 00:33:13.900
Just not Meng Guangcai's company.

00:33:17.160 --> 00:33:18.420
Huifen, all these years, I...

00:33:19.660 --> 00:33:21.380
I've watched Qianqian
grow up day by day.

00:33:21.539 --> 00:33:23.519
I don't know when she'll suddenly ask me

00:33:25.000 --> 00:33:27.019
when her father's case will be solved

00:33:29.160 --> 00:33:31.180
and when I'll give her father justice.

00:33:34.599 --> 00:33:36.400
I dread those questions.

00:33:40.700 --> 00:33:41.579
Huifen,

00:33:42.400 --> 00:33:45.180
I also know, all these years,
the person I've wronged the most is you.

00:33:47.000 --> 00:33:48.500
You've suffered so much with me.

00:33:49.400 --> 00:33:50.779
I've wronged you.

00:34:10.739 --> 00:34:12.199
Hello, here's your dish.

00:34:13.340 --> 00:34:14.239
Made up your mind?

00:34:17.039 --> 00:34:19.500
If I sign, do I really get the money?

00:34:21.019 --> 00:34:24.539
Sign today, and this 300,000 is yours.

00:34:27.280 --> 00:34:30.760
Really, 300,000?
You're not lying to me, are you?

00:34:36.139 --> 00:34:38.400
Have some coffee.

00:34:38.400 --> 00:34:39.000
Thanks.

00:34:41.980 --> 00:34:42.900
You don't understand.

00:34:43.099 --> 00:34:46.079
My old man won't leave me a single cent.

00:34:46.320 --> 00:34:49.380
And I'm desperate for cash.
I need it to bounce back, alright?

00:34:49.800 --> 00:34:52.780
I'm still his son.
And that house has my share, right?

00:34:53.400 --> 00:34:56.599
If I don't sign, who will, right?

00:34:57.320 --> 00:34:58.300
Is this the...

00:35:00.179 --> 00:35:01.460
Yes, take a look.

00:35:06.855 --> 00:35:07.456
(Compensation Agreement)

00:35:09.420 --> 00:35:11.159
I'm signing it.

00:35:11.159 --> 00:35:11.980
Read it carefully.

00:35:12.320 --> 00:35:15.199
It's fine, I trust you. I'll sign it.

00:35:17.079 --> 00:35:17.719
Not so fast.

00:35:18.579 --> 00:35:21.860
Tomorrow, I need you
to do one more thing for me.

00:35:33.500 --> 00:35:36.760
Good. That's the spirit. Very smooth.

00:35:37.019 --> 00:35:38.280
Can we make it even smoother?

00:35:38.599 --> 00:35:39.159
Got it.

00:35:51.780 --> 00:35:53.440
What are you doing, Dad? Dad!

00:35:53.679 --> 00:35:55.539
Come back, Dad! Come back!

00:35:55.539 --> 00:35:56.860
That's dangerous.

00:35:56.860 --> 00:35:59.599
Go. Just go. Get out of here.
I don't need you!

00:36:00.199 --> 00:36:02.159
Even if you kill me,
I'm tearing this place down.

00:36:02.480 --> 00:36:05.639
Money's settled.
What are you doing, Dad?

00:36:05.639 --> 00:36:06.639
Everything's gone.

00:36:06.639 --> 00:36:08.199
Qin, it's all thanks to you.

00:36:08.199 --> 00:36:10.880
It only took a few days
to get it signed.

00:36:12.820 --> 00:36:16.460
The 'filial' son.
And this good son also helped.

00:36:18.440 --> 00:36:19.019
Let's go.

00:36:22.019 --> 00:36:22.719
Dad!

00:36:24.280 --> 00:36:26.119
Dad. Dad.

00:36:27.139 --> 00:36:29.079
Dad, listen to me.

00:36:29.079 --> 00:36:30.119
Once the place is down,

00:36:30.280 --> 00:36:32.920
they'll give us the money.
Then we'll have cash.

00:36:32.920 --> 00:36:34.400
- You go.
- What are you doing?

00:36:34.400 --> 00:36:36.280
I need a place to retire.

00:36:36.280 --> 00:36:37.480
Don't do this, Dad.

00:36:37.780 --> 00:36:40.480
It's already settled.
Let them tear it down.

00:36:40.960 --> 00:36:41.940
What are you doing?

00:37:05.000 --> 00:37:07.880
Yes. The demolition work
is basically complete.

00:37:08.780 --> 00:37:11.139
The follow-up construction is all ready.

00:37:12.000 --> 00:37:12.800
Rest assured.

00:37:13.579 --> 00:37:15.960
I'm heading to the site now
to arrange the restart.

00:37:16.159 --> 00:37:18.599
And tonight,
I'll report to you in person.

00:37:20.000 --> 00:37:21.699
Okay. Talk later then.

00:37:35.480 --> 00:37:36.199
Zhu?

00:37:38.099 --> 00:37:40.179
Long time no see. What are you...

00:37:40.679 --> 00:37:43.960
I couldn't find you at your office.
I had to track you down to your car.

00:37:46.219 --> 00:37:47.179
What is it? Go ahead.

00:37:47.599 --> 00:37:48.840
We received a report.

00:37:49.260 --> 00:37:53.000
It said you went behind the resident
and tricked his son into signing a deal.

00:37:55.019 --> 00:37:55.960
That matter?

00:37:57.719 --> 00:38:00.880
I can't deal with it right now.
Can we talk next time?

00:38:00.980 --> 00:38:02.360
The father and son fought.

00:38:02.579 --> 00:38:04.440
The old man
is still lying in the hospital.

00:38:04.800 --> 00:38:06.900
You don't have time? Well, I do.

00:38:06.900 --> 00:38:07.679
I'm handling this.

00:38:09.420 --> 00:38:12.820
I really have urgent business.
Now's not the time for this.

00:38:14.000 --> 00:38:16.619
You go ahead. We'll talk on the way.

00:38:17.260 --> 00:38:18.079
I'm coming with you.

00:38:37.280 --> 00:38:38.579
To investigate me,

00:38:39.679 --> 00:38:41.480
you even came along on my errand.

00:38:46.599 --> 00:38:50.800
Back in the day,
I thought you were a hero

00:38:51.519 --> 00:38:53.940
and a good big brother.
I listened to you

00:38:54.820 --> 00:38:56.019
and left Shaguai Village

00:38:56.639 --> 00:38:59.800
to find a way out for myself
and for the brothers.

00:39:00.800 --> 00:39:01.699
But you?

00:39:02.699 --> 00:39:04.500
From the moment
I started my small business,

00:39:05.460 --> 00:39:06.980
you've watched me like a hawk,

00:39:07.460 --> 00:39:08.960
investigating me openly and secretly.

00:39:10.400 --> 00:39:11.199
I'm telling you,

00:39:12.900 --> 00:39:13.888
I didn't break the law.

00:39:16.000 --> 00:39:17.300
And I won't.

00:39:20.179 --> 00:39:21.460
Like I said earlier,

00:39:21.639 --> 00:39:24.280
that demolition agreement
was signed with the family.

00:39:25.579 --> 00:39:28.179
And I paid the money
according to the rules.

00:39:30.199 --> 00:39:31.679
Now the father and son are fighting.

00:39:32.800 --> 00:39:36.460
What does such a trivial matter
have to do with me?

00:39:37.000 --> 00:39:37.639
Zhu.

00:39:38.940 --> 00:39:39.500
No.

00:39:41.960 --> 00:39:42.760
Officer Zhu,

00:39:47.920 --> 00:39:49.639
do you know what situation I'm in now?

00:39:53.219 --> 00:39:54.800
The knife's already at my throat.

00:39:56.960 --> 00:39:58.019
Lives are at stake.

00:40:00.900 --> 00:40:02.260
We've known each other for years.

00:40:03.820 --> 00:40:07.320
What's your beef with me exactly?

00:40:08.440 --> 00:40:11.719
You called that trivial.
How is that trivial?

00:40:12.599 --> 00:40:15.199
For a family,
it's a life-shattering event.

00:40:17.099 --> 00:40:18.539
What's exactly my beef with you?

00:40:19.280 --> 00:40:23.780
The words you just spoke shouldn't be
from the Meng Guangcai of Shaguai Village.

00:40:25.320 --> 00:40:26.119
Officer,

00:40:26.960 --> 00:40:28.940
no matter what it is,
I'll ask you one more time:

00:40:29.139 --> 00:40:32.159
What does it have to do with me?

00:40:32.159 --> 00:40:33.579
It has nothing to do with you now.

00:40:33.659 --> 00:40:37.500
Fine. Even if you are clever enough
to skirt the law.

00:40:37.500 --> 00:40:39.460
But do you have a clear conscience?

00:40:40.000 --> 00:40:42.079
Every word you say is about yourself.

00:40:42.320 --> 00:40:44.039
Have you considered how others feel?

00:40:45.280 --> 00:40:47.320
Enough with the lectures.

00:40:48.099 --> 00:40:49.888
You couldn't help me
back in Shaguai Village.

00:40:51.400 --> 00:40:53.380
You couldn't help me
at Baima Market either.

00:40:54.619 --> 00:40:57.960
Now you show up and give me the lecture.

00:40:59.039 --> 00:41:00.539
You're such a great big brother.

00:41:09.619 --> 00:41:10.260
He's here.

00:41:11.039 --> 00:41:12.599
- Get out!
- Get out!

00:41:13.179 --> 00:41:17.480
- Get out!
- Get out! Get out!

00:41:20.699 --> 00:41:21.820
- Pay up!
- Pay up!

00:41:21.820 --> 00:41:23.900
No! Stop!

00:41:24.440 --> 00:41:25.280
Listen to me.

00:41:25.280 --> 00:41:25.980
Pay up first!

00:41:25.980 --> 00:41:27.420
You'll get every cent.

00:41:27.599 --> 00:41:29.699
We agreed. I'm here today to pay, okay?

00:41:29.699 --> 00:41:32.659
If you don't pay today,
we'll smash this car!

00:41:35.280 --> 00:41:36.039
Smash this car!

00:41:37.300 --> 00:41:38.179
Smash it!

00:41:38.699 --> 00:41:39.199
Smash!

00:41:44.019 --> 00:41:44.519
Stop it!

00:41:54.360 --> 00:41:55.920
Break it up! Break it up!

00:41:57.420 --> 00:41:59.079
Stop it! Move!

00:41:59.400 --> 00:42:00.039
Break it up!

00:42:03.880 --> 00:42:06.480
Meng Guangcai,
I'm copying your old trick.

00:42:08.119 --> 00:42:08.780
Pay up!

00:42:12.159 --> 00:42:15.000
Police! Police! Police!

00:42:17.500 --> 00:42:18.159
Police!

00:42:36.039 --> 00:42:36.679
- Guangcai.
- Guangcai.

00:42:38.420 --> 00:42:41.500
Stop waiting. The clients heard
about what happened at the site.

00:42:41.500 --> 00:42:43.232
They're not coming.
Said it's too sensitive.

00:42:43.400 --> 00:42:44.704
They told us to be careful too.

00:42:46.760 --> 00:42:49.380
We can't afford any more trouble
with the demolition.

00:43:12.880 --> 00:43:15.480
Did you get anything on those
troublemakers from this afternoon?

00:43:15.800 --> 00:43:19.300
Cops hauled them in, chewed them out.
And then they bolted.

00:43:19.699 --> 00:43:21.119
I've found them all with our men.

00:43:21.260 --> 00:43:21.800
Good.

00:43:22.820 --> 00:43:23.780
Now that they're found,

00:43:24.360 --> 00:43:25.199
don't hold back.

00:43:26.460 --> 00:43:27.519
We're not the police.

00:43:28.280 --> 00:43:28.920
Understood.

00:43:56.539 --> 00:44:00.079
Dazhu, tell our men to keep it discreet.
Don't disturb anyone.

00:44:00.440 --> 00:44:01.480
Got it.

00:44:02.460 --> 00:44:04.900
You guys, watch the back door.

00:44:05.059 --> 00:44:06.920
You guys, watch the front.

00:44:06.920 --> 00:44:08.420
The rest go with Guangcai.

00:44:18.699 --> 00:44:19.539
Don't worry.

00:44:19.800 --> 00:44:22.320
Anything Beiyan-related, just tell me.

00:44:22.320 --> 00:44:25.500
No problem. It can all be handled.

00:44:26.099 --> 00:44:26.619
Come in.

00:44:27.719 --> 00:44:29.900
Okay, okay.

00:44:31.199 --> 00:44:31.820
What is this?

00:44:34.159 --> 00:44:35.639
Meng Guangcai?

00:44:38.500 --> 00:44:39.940
What's going on? What's this?

00:44:40.619 --> 00:44:42.960
Meng Guangcai, what are you doing?
What's this?

00:44:43.099 --> 00:44:43.900
What's this?

00:44:44.980 --> 00:44:46.820
Didn't you want me
to give you whatever I have?

00:44:47.699 --> 00:44:48.780
You were so impatient?

00:44:49.940 --> 00:44:51.699
Putting on a show
at my construction site?

00:44:53.280 --> 00:44:55.820
Alright. You've tracked me down?

00:44:56.460 --> 00:44:57.472
What do you want?

00:44:58.880 --> 00:44:59.960
To celebrate with you.

00:44:59.960 --> 00:45:02.260
Celebrate what?
Don't pull this stunt on me.

00:45:02.260 --> 00:45:04.500
Before I call the police,
take your people and get out.

00:45:04.679 --> 00:45:06.539
Get out. Go. Call security.

00:45:06.940 --> 00:45:08.199
Call the police.

00:45:10.039 --> 00:45:11.480
Trying this with me?

00:45:12.460 --> 00:45:13.000
Hello?

00:45:16.940 --> 00:45:18.940
Call him 'boss.' Call him.

00:45:20.360 --> 00:45:21.039
Boss.

00:45:22.260 --> 00:45:24.039
Here's one who assaulted an officer.

00:45:24.800 --> 00:45:26.940
How much did he pay you? How much?

00:45:27.280 --> 00:45:28.280
Talk!

00:45:29.199 --> 00:45:29.780
50,000.

00:45:30.960 --> 00:45:35.719
50,000 to deal with us?
The men you hired aren't exactly pros.

00:45:37.599 --> 00:45:39.980
What? I didn't know about this.

00:45:39.980 --> 00:45:42.199
When did I give you 50,000?

00:45:42.420 --> 00:45:44.019
Do I even know you? Why would I pay you?

00:45:44.300 --> 00:45:47.519
July 15, 1999, gift to Zhang:

00:45:48.019 --> 00:45:50.679
1.2 million RMB.

00:45:51.900 --> 00:45:56.199
May 7, 2000, gift to Liu: RMB 800,000

00:45:56.199 --> 00:45:58.199
and ten 50-gram gold bars.

00:45:58.280 --> 00:46:02.960
December 31, 2001, gift to Wang:
RMB 2,000,000

00:46:03.119 --> 00:46:04.440
and USD 80,000.

00:46:04.960 --> 00:46:06.579
January 8, 2002...

00:46:06.960 --> 00:46:10.039
Bro, stop it. Stop it.

00:46:10.039 --> 00:46:13.539
Mr. Nian, do you admit to these?
Should I keep reading?

00:46:13.960 --> 00:46:14.679
No.

00:46:18.079 --> 00:46:18.760
Mr. Nian,

00:46:19.900 --> 00:46:21.152
weren't you calling the cops?

00:46:21.400 --> 00:46:24.920
You had men cause trouble
and beat people at my construction site.

00:46:25.440 --> 00:46:28.000
Let's see whom the police will arrest.
You or me?

00:46:31.820 --> 00:46:33.940
Mr. Meng, Mr. Meng.

00:46:34.119 --> 00:46:36.880
Mr. Meng, it's all a misunderstanding.

00:46:37.119 --> 00:46:40.260
From the start, I knew
you were a man of substance, Mr. Meng.

00:46:40.260 --> 00:46:42.619
See? You really are a man of substance.

00:46:42.900 --> 00:46:45.659
I deeply admire you.
It's all a misunderstanding.

00:46:45.659 --> 00:46:46.960
Later, your men

00:46:46.960 --> 00:46:48.699
should stay. Let me treat you all.

00:46:48.699 --> 00:46:50.800
We can sit down
and talk this through properly.

00:46:52.820 --> 00:46:54.199
Mr. Meng, this is not appropriate.

00:46:54.199 --> 00:46:56.820
There are so many people at my company.

00:46:56.820 --> 00:47:00.159
We can skip this.
Let's just sit and talk.

00:47:02.000 --> 00:47:05.960
How about this? I'll pull out
of the Baima project, okay?

00:47:05.960 --> 00:47:08.880
If the city asks my opinion,
I'll say Caisheng can handle it well.

00:47:08.880 --> 00:47:11.760
I'll be a guidance unit.
Is that acceptable?

00:47:13.320 --> 00:47:14.159
Mr. Meng,

00:47:15.500 --> 00:47:16.380
okay?

00:47:16.980 --> 00:47:17.619
Okay.

00:47:18.900 --> 00:47:20.579
We can discuss anything, right?

00:47:38.656 --> 00:47:42.177
(Biaojie Construction)

00:47:54.619 --> 00:47:55.960
Let's go. Get in the car.

00:48:02.199 --> 00:48:03.199
What did you do?

00:48:03.480 --> 00:48:04.400
Nothing.

00:48:06.099 --> 00:48:09.179
Demolition's done,
and the site's reopened.

00:48:09.559 --> 00:48:11.380
So I set off some firecrackers
to celebrate.

00:48:11.539 --> 00:48:12.768
I helped you at the site

00:48:13.888 --> 00:48:15.260
because I didn't want you hurt.

00:48:16.039 --> 00:48:17.340
Not so you could show off here.

00:48:17.920 --> 00:48:21.019
If that guy broke the law,
he should be handed over to the police.

00:48:21.639 --> 00:48:22.619
Broke the law?

00:48:23.219 --> 00:48:26.500
No, Zhu, no one broke the law.

00:48:26.760 --> 00:48:29.139
If you don't believe me,
go upstairs and ask him.

00:48:29.539 --> 00:48:33.699
I'm telling the truth.
I just came to celebrate with him.

00:48:43.019 --> 00:48:43.860
Zhu,

00:48:45.000 --> 00:48:47.719
you helped me. I really am grateful.

00:48:48.599 --> 00:48:53.679
But some things can't be solved
by your moral high ground preaching.

00:49:00.579 --> 00:49:01.199
Guangcai,

00:49:07.599 --> 00:49:08.300
trouble.

00:49:10.159 --> 00:49:12.000
It's the demolition. Someone's jumping.

00:49:12.000 --> 00:49:12.860
He's at the hospital.

00:49:24.579 --> 00:49:26.280
The weather's turned so quickly.

00:49:48.019 --> 00:49:48.840
What do we do?

00:49:48.840 --> 00:49:50.000
Someone, help him.

00:49:52.000 --> 00:49:53.179
It's pouring rain.

00:49:54.980 --> 00:49:56.960
If his body gives out or he slips...

00:49:57.400 --> 00:49:58.460
Move aside.

00:49:58.699 --> 00:49:59.199
What now?

00:50:03.079 --> 00:50:05.000
Is this the 'trivial matter' you said?

00:50:09.480 --> 00:50:12.300
Guangcai, the project is crucial.
We can't afford more trouble.

00:50:25.119 --> 00:50:26.699
Go. Get more people.

00:50:27.039 --> 00:50:28.500
And contain any reporters.

00:50:29.599 --> 00:50:31.099
Sir. Sir.

00:50:32.280 --> 00:50:34.420
I'm a police officer, sir.

00:50:35.219 --> 00:50:37.360
Please come down. We can work it out.

00:50:37.800 --> 00:50:39.460
Easy now. Come down.

00:50:39.460 --> 00:50:41.300
We can talk it through. I'll listen.

00:50:41.300 --> 00:50:43.019
Tell me what's wrong.

00:50:47.039 --> 00:50:49.360
My late wife left nothing behind.

00:50:50.039 --> 00:50:54.000
Only this house.
And you people tore it down.

00:50:54.000 --> 00:50:55.940
Sir, look.

00:50:55.940 --> 00:50:57.360
When in trouble, call the police.

00:50:57.500 --> 00:50:58.360
Am I right?

00:50:58.360 --> 00:51:00.460
Whatever it is,
come down and let's talk it over.

00:51:00.579 --> 00:51:02.820
No problem is too big. I am a cop.

00:51:03.099 --> 00:51:04.920
Tell me what's bothering you.

00:51:06.159 --> 00:51:08.300
Talk to me. I'll help you resolve it.

00:51:22.700 --> 00:51:27.724
=The Silent Rift=